{"tid":1185830,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)叮噹劇場版3","createTime":"2019-06-04T13:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T17:53:31.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cf2bb69999f60dcba55e938cc58a4cceae18f5ed","tid":1185830,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CguBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=b63a5f72\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CguBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=200512eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CguBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=4d3e0976\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61hCom-u5KL._SY445_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F61hCom-u5KL._SY445_.jpg&h=f8cf0952&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://images-fe.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51SS0KGJSBL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-fe.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F51SS0KGJSBL.jpg&h=3ae59d4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w533_and_h300_bestv2/vSEkT7GxEoVkzNszj6rb9KCBwwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.tmdb.org%2Ft%2Fp%2Fw533_and_h300_bestv2%2FvSEkT7GxEoVkzNszj6rb9KCBwwq.jpg&h=08aaf818&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://cdn.www.tsutaya.co.jp/images/jacket/05355/4988104027412_1L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.www.tsutaya.co.jp%2Fimages%2Fjacket%2F05355%2F4988104027412_1L.jpg&h=80cda8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://blog-imgs-81.fc2.com/p/e/p/peperonnoyousai/mugengohan2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-81.fc2.com%2Fp%2Fe%2Fp%2Fpeperonnoyousai%2Fmugengohan2.jpg&h=0b2f1c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n動物惑星:某天夜晚，大雄從一片粉紅色的霧氣裡（後來得知是22世紀的任意瓦斯，動物們稱為光之梯）進入一片從未見過的森林，在那裡動物用人的語言交流，而且都是直立行走。次日，大雄將這件事告訴同學，大家笑他是「在發童話世界的夢」。儘管大雄拿了一朵從夢境裡帶來的花，一樣無人相信。同時，開發商有將後山興建成為高爾夫球場的計劃。那個夜晚，大雄再次進入那片森林，原來那不是夢，而是一個動物星球<br />\n<br />\n天方夜譚:有一次大雄他們用哆啦A夢的道具進入畫冊的世界，但靜香途中丟了回現實世界的鞋子所以被捉去當奴隷，且畫冊又被媽媽燒掉，便用時光機返回古代阿拉伯世界尋找靜香，途中乘船航行時，更被船上的水手和盜賊們丟到大海中，之後在黃金宮殿中遇上辛巴達，而拯救靜香後，盜賊們又來壞事<br />\n<br />\n雲之國:因為相信雲上有天國存在的大雄，去圖書館找資料（全都是神話故事），後來想離家出走，去找天國，目前要令哆啦A夢擔心他，後來哆啦A夢和大雄在雲上建造一個自己理想中的國家，並且在朋友們的協助下完成了王國。但是，某天在氣流的影響下，撞到高山，發現了一個男孩（塔卡洛）在一隻有耳的巨型烏龜（後來得知是絕跡的雕齒獸）的背上，最後卻意外發現真的有天上人居住的天上世界..<br />\n<br />\n迷宮之旅:又到了春假，大雄約定與爸爸去白金飯店。大雄本來非常高興，但是卻不知道飯店的實際位置。而一個神秘手提箱送到了大雄的家裡，大雄通過這個手提箱來到了白金飯店。本來大雄與哆啦A夢在島上愉快的玩耍，但是哆啦A夢卻突然失蹤了，原來哆啦A夢被神秘的火箭載走了..<br />\n<br />\n魔域三劍俠:現實世界裡的大雄一事無成，利用哆啦A夢的造夢機，在夢境世界卻成為英雄劍士，與妖怪軍團作戰，但是夢境漸漸與現實交錯，發生不可思議的事情..<br />\n<br />\n9 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CguBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=53eb127e\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CguBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=e5d268c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ff202a7ab4fbd54a4bc4377b9bf8692e4a5b3f","tid":1185830,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T14:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf584c28f5edb0610e15a15ccc5d4c4ca552409","tid":1185830,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32e14a9f12495439210fbc67a6372d787fb91b1","tid":1185830,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fead15d68c05f6c2c3590fadfe8d0800c8e128","tid":1185830,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T16:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456bf5afae71996e3ff56b25eb328fe8448aae52","tid":1185830,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b829f06c1e52a78048584d517c6124f170aee78a","tid":1185830,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}